<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Shrub or small tree up to 2.5 m tall; sparingly to much branched; branches thick; stems strong and flexible; leaves clustered terminally; lanceolate 6-10 
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
0.5-1 cm; flowers white.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
